12,345 would return 5 plus 3 plus 1. And for a number

00:01:10.809 --> 00:01:16.230
like 6,789, would return 9 plus 7. I'll give

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:19.330
you the code for summing all the digits to start with. And there will be

